document_data.name: Maluradek
document_data.mainbody: '''Maluradek''' was one of the noble houses of ancient [[Anauria]].
document_data.Members: It was one of three [[human]] houses that composed Anauria's nobility, along with [[House Nemrin]] and the royal [[House Thardresk]].
document_data.History: ''Circa'' the [[Era of Upheaval]], some traces of House Maluradek could be found amongst the ruins of Anauria, scattered across the [[Anauroch]] desert.
